>\n早知揀civil <br />\n1d刺激感都冇 <br />\n我直頭係話 <br />\n好似輕鬆d</blockquote><br />\n好彩你冇簡civil"},{"pid":"117ccdf3b4bded164d9309a94200cd09f48c1f69","tid":318223,"uid":83676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T04:02:39.000Z","msg":"樓豬on9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nive不嬲都係咁in架啦"},{"pid":"4b1e8ef0bef7dc203400d92e527c402caa94682d","tid":318223,"uid":36770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T04:05:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓豬on9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nive不嬲都係咁in架啦</blockquote><br />\n屌你，我又未讀過ive，點撚知呢d野"},{"pid":"b39b6b64cc0a76bcd6dfdedc3419eabe8c854d0f","tid":318223,"uid":35408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T04:07:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓豬on9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nive不嬲都係咁in架啦</blockquote><br />\n首批會考失敗者<br />\n再報咗幾次ive都讀唔成嘅經驗"},{"pid":"9e86059b378ee190444469f4a9df881c4405ee6b","tid":318223,"uid":43309,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T04:09:01.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">樓主係大陸狗黎(已自認)</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/12/161112_2d962b7cb80e281c2fa2573829c89a1e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F12%2F161112_2d962b7cb80e281c2fa2573829c89a1e.jpg&h=4ed886d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">呢個係樓主之前個名-連尼住(大佬)</span></strong></span><br />\n讀垃圾OU HD，打字用拼音。<br />\n之後俾巴打圍屌，死不悔改之餘，<br />\n仲笑鳩人讀書少，唔抵得人識打拼音！<br />\n堅稱自己係土生土長嘅香港人喎~~<br />\n樓主用拼音打字證據：<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=0B62Ifzhk_YNaNVFfSFlRekZnclU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D0B62Ifzhk_YNaNVFfSFlRekZnclU&d=tVQayoMpeeFv0KaNZAnvlqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=90176f65\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=0B62Ifzhk_YNaNVFfSFlRekZnclU</a><br />\n<br />\n日期：2017-1-10<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就算識打字嗰陣都要轉channel去諗嗰個字嘅蝗語點讀，再打出嚟。<br />\n點都慢過用倉頡速成就咁諗點打好撚多<br />\n除非佢本身就係蝗語channel，又或者講慣蝗語<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/12/163227_7529c4fae71b5dd7ff9beea275ef5ec9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F12%2F163227_7529c4fae71b5dd7ff9beea275ef5ec9.jpg&h=ca5c499d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根本係大陸仔打啲字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又唸又窩又奔，都唔知佢打乜柒！<br />\n你全家奔緊落地獄呀支那狗！！！！！<br />\n下世咪撚再落黎香港，生生世世做中蟈人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n經過追擊之下，終於承認自己係支那狗，<br />\n並聲稱自己永遠都唔上LIHKG<br />\n又改名-你仲唔仆街<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/15/233117_e7fca3f6eec812664dffae026e0b271d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F15%2F233117_e7fca3f6eec812664dffae026e0b271d.jpg&h=443b5ea8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但好景不常，經過一個月潛水又俾我見返佢！<br />\n所以只好繼續我嘅追擊行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n條柒頭份人極度陰險，之前開post叫雞俾人放飛機開post起人底！<br />\n<br />\n小心呢件ptgf<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/77362/page/1?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/77362/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n<br />\n仲話叫ptgf唔係叫雞喎，你咪撚玩啦！<br />\n人地唔撚so你好出奇咩？<br />\n雞都嫌棄你賤種畜生呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係咁多先，希望樓主真係好好守承諾，<br />\n唔好再上黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>條賤種拎強姦慘劇黎講笑<br />\n聲稱要合法化強姦十點後外出嘅女人</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/237323/page/1?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/237323/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n<br />\n你喺網上唔代表可以乜都講<br />\n你上得連登就代表你係一個人<br />\n唔該你地似返個人<br />\n認撚住條雞蟲份人係幾撚低劣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4642b257755838739e0ff7bb53afecd42713677","tid":318223,"uid":7285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T04:09:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>入工程it幼教藥劑，其他好伏<br />\n<br />\n簡間大同設施好既校社，否則呢2年會後悔<br />\n<br />\nPS: 畢業生</blockquote><br />\n好彩，青衣 N展<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n除左civil bse 其他都搵唔到工<br />\n<br />\n利申hr</blockquote><br />\n唔好吹咁大wo清<br />\n幼教同<span style=\"color: red;\">藥劑</span>都搵到工</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 班友屌曬鬼話中伏喇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nIVE將以前出名嘅藥劑斬開左幾科黎呃錢，揀撚錯就中伏"},{"pid":"8983ca422d989112d97dabcf6bc5305139b7dcd9","tid":318223,"uid":16799,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T04:12:33.000Z","msg":"Ive姐 都要準備？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba115ccb54163777b437ebbe9097b055a01202da","tid":318223,"uid":37942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T04:17:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認真面試又話 i大都要in<br />\nhea你又話hea</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b40b8892a76b903c28f8b63d7582697c15295e3","tid":318223,"uid":51825,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T04:26:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/201